answers.body_markdown:
Your constructor is malformed.
This line

    this.crimeStatus = crimeStatus;

Doesn&#39;t do anything as long as the list of parameters is missing that property.

Change

    public CrimeData(String location, String crimeType, String crimeDetails) {

To

    public CrimeData(String location, String crimeType, String crimeDetails, String crimeStatus) {

The same goes for the usage of the constructor:

    CrimeData crimeData = new CrimeData(location, crimeType, crimeDetails);

Should be

    CrimeData crimeData = new CrimeData(location, crimeType, crimeDetails, crimeStatus);

